Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.16,0:00:47.29,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果那些人是普通人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.59,0:00:49.47,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,小红就没办法得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.01,0:00:54.12,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,我无论怎么感谢都觉得不够呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,06
